{NORTH has lots of points - 26 to be exact. She opens 2\C. 
In the old days this hand would have been opened 3NT.

SOUTH has 4 points and responds 2\D.

NORTH now shows her full strength by jumping to 3NT (25-27 points, balanced).

SOUTH knows there is no slam, so he passes 3NT.}

