[Student "S"]
{EAST has 22 points and opens 2\C.

WEST is pretty weak, right? She responds 2\D.

EAST bids his suit, 2\H.

WEST is so weak she bids the second negative - 3\C.

EAST rebids his suit, 3\H, and WEST passes.}

