{EAST opens 2\C and is pleased when WEST makes a positive response of 2\S. 
His first step is to set the trump suit by bidding 3\S. There is NO chance that WEST will pass.

WEST now bids 4\C a Control-showing bid. 
EAST continues Control-showing with 4\D.

That's enough for WEST to hear. She invokes Blackwood and learning they have all the Aces 
bids 7\S.}

